## Sequencing note
This is a large multi-repo change. Recommend treating each phase as a hard checkpoint —
confirm the backend is deployed/verified working (including running the migration
script yourself) before starting Phase 2, and Phase 2 verified before Phase 3 — rather
than implementing all three in one uninterrupted pass.